- A trip's duration is calculated as the difference between the end time and the start time, converted to minutes; 
- Vehicle maintenance records are considered only if they occurred within the last 12 months; 
- Average trip duration and average fare are calculated based on all trips for each route, regardless of the vehicle used.

sql:
SELECT route_name
FROM routes
WHERE route_length = (SELECT MAX(route_length) FROM routes);
